metadata.name: Children playing with a tuktuk, Marpha, 2022
metadata.description: The Himalaya mountains are home to 53 million people. Most of its population live in small towns or villages like the one in which this photo was taken : Marpha. Curiously, on this day many children where wondering about in the streets and playing with all kind of objects they could find. Here, they were 3, running in and out of this tuktuk, making the street a perfect playground for them.
